Time Series

- Sequence of data usually collected at regular intervals
- daily/ monthly/ yearly

Financial Domain
- unemployment, GDP, daily exchange, share prices

Analyse TS data and plan future stratehy

-------------
TS is very unpredictable in nature. Need to decompose the TS into components
Trend - long term movements
Seasonal - cyclical fluctuations related periodical fluctuations : period - month/qtr of year; can be identified by plotting
Cycles  - associated with longer period business cycles
Residues/ Irregular : systematic patterns / random noise 